OL,3,CWho is vying for the Scottish
OL,4,CConservative leadership?
OL,6,FThree MSPs have secured the
OL,7,Fnominations needed to run for the
OL,8,FScottish Conservative leadership and
OL,9,Fsucceed Douglas Ross.
OL,11,FRussell Findlay, Murdo Fraser and
OL,12,FMeghan Gallacher will take part in
OL,13,Ftheir first hustings event on Saturday
OL,14,Fas Tory members prepare to choose the
OL,15,Fnew leader.
OL,17,FAll three have promised to revive the
OL,18,Ffortunes of the Tories north of the
OL,19,Fborder, after the party's vote share
OL,20,Fat the General Election slumped to
OL,21,Fhalf what it was in 2019.
