OL,3,CWho is vying for the Scottish
OL,4,CConservative leadership?
OL,6,FAs one of the 2021 entrants to
OL,7,FHolyrood, he has challenged the
OL,8,FGovernment on a number of issues
OL,9,Faround crime and justice, campaigning
OL,10,Fwhich has boosted his profile in
OL,11,FScottish politics.
OL,13,FHis supporters are keen to highlight
OL,14,Fhis past career as an investigative
OL,15,Fjournalist working to expose organised
OL,16,Fcrime.
OL,18,FIn 2015 he suffered an acid attack on
OL,19,Fhis doorstep but fought back and was
OL,20,Fable to pin down his assailant until
OL,21,Fpolice arrived.
