OL,3,CWho is vying for the Scottish
OL,4,CConservative leadership?
OL,6,FMurdo Fraser, 58, is the longest-
OL,7,Fserving Tory MSP, having been in
OL,8,FHolyrood since 2001.
OL,10,FAt his campaign launch in Perth, two
OL,11,Fother leadership contenders ` Jamie
OL,12,FGreene and Liam Kerr ` dropped their
OL,13,Fown bids to instead back him. Brian
OL,14,FWhittle, another early leadership
OL,15,Fchallenger, had already done the same.
OL,17,FMr Fraser has called on his remaining
OL,18,Fopponents to join his team,
OL,19,Fessentially seeking for the race to
OL,20,Fbecome a coronation.
